description: The SPDR SSGA Multi-Asset Real Return ETF seeks to achieve real return consisting of capital appreciation and current income. Seeks to provide exposure to domestic and international inflation protected securities, real estate securities, commodities, infrastructure companies, and companies in natural resources and/or commodity businesses which may include agriculture, energy, and metals and mining companies as well as industrial, and utility companies.The investment process relies on a proprietary quantitative model as well as fundamental views regarding factors that may not be captured by the quantitative model
name: SPDR SSGA Multi-Asset Real Return ETF
